19#include "ODUPCEANReader.h"

21namespace ZXing {
22namespace OneD {
23
24/**
25* <p>Implements decoding of the EAN-13 format.</p>
26*
27* @author dswitkin@google.com (Daniel Switkin)
28* @author Sean Owen
29* @author alasdair@google.com (Alasdair Mackintosh)
30*/
31class EAN13Reader : public UPCEANReader
32{
33public:
34 explicit EAN13Reader(const DecodeHints& hints) : UPCEANReader(hints) {}
35
36 BarcodeFormat expectedFormat() const override;
37 BitArray::Range decodeMiddle(const BitArray& row, BitArray::Iterator begin, std::string& resultString) const override;
38};
